OL,3,CConsumer confidence improves but
OL,4,Cremains subdued ahead of Christmas
OL,6,FConsumer confidence edged up ahead of
OL,7,FChristmas but remains subdued in the
OL,8,Fface of cost-of-living pressures,
OL,9,Faccording to new figures.
OL,11,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,12,FIndex improved by two points to minus
OL,13,F17 for December.
OL,15,FThe research showed that all five of
OL,16,Fthe survey's measures increased for
OL,17,Fthe month, bouncing back from a weak
OL,18,FNovember which had been impacted by
OL,19,Fpre-Budget caution.
