OL,3,CConsumer confidence improves but
OL,4,Cremains subdued ahead of Christmas
OL,6,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,7,Fdirector at GfK, said: "It's tempting
OL,8,Fto see festive cheer in December's two-
OL,9,Fpoint improvement in consumer
OL,10,Fconfidence.
OL,12,F"This is a surprise finding for the UK
OL,13,Fhigh street because it contrasts with
OL,14,Fthe Black Friday sales slump we
OL,15,Freported on earlier this month."
OL,17,FIndustry data pointed to weakness on
OL,18,Fthe high street earlier in the run-up
OL,19,Fto Christmas, the data from the CBI
OL,20,Fshowing the sharpest fall in sentiment
OL,21,Famong retailers for 17 years.
