OL,3,CConsumer confidence improves but
OL,4,Cremains subdued ahead of Christmas
OL,6,FThe GfK figures showed a four-point
OL,7,Fimprovement in its major purchase
OL,8,Findex ` an indicator of confidence in
OL,9,Fbuying big ticket items ` to minus 11.
OL,11,FMeasures related to shoppers' views
OL,12,Fabout the wider economic outlook also
OL,13,Fimproved slightly for the month.
OL,15,FMr Bellamy said: "UK households still
OL,16,Fface cost-of-living pressures, despite
OL,17,Fthe recent softening in inflation,
OL,18,Falong with rising economic
OL,19,Funcertainty, and those conditions
OL,20,Fresult in weaker consumer confidence.
